@startuml

[*] -> Idle

Idle --> Login : Open App / Website
Login --> Login : Invalid Credentials
Login --> Authenticated : Valid Credentials
Authenticated --> Dashboard

Dashboard --> Transaction : Transfer / Pay Bill
Dashboard --> AccountManagement : Update Profile / Change Password
Dashboard --> ViewBalance : Select "View Balance"
Dashboard --> Logout : Logout Request

Transaction --> Dashboard : Success
Transaction --> Error : Failure

Error --> Dashboard : Retry
Error --> Login : Session Expired
Dashboard --> Login : Session Expired

Logout --> Idle

@enduml